    SELECT [l].[Id], [l].[AssignedUserId], [l].[BuildingName], [l].[BuildingNo], [l].[Code], [l].[CreatedById], [l].[CreatedDate], [l].[CustomFields], [l].[DMSubNumber], [l].[Date], [l].[DeleteDate], [l].[IsActive], [l].[IsDelete], [l].[LandNumber], [l].[Mobile], [l].[ModifiedById], [l].[ModifiedDate], [l].[Name], [l].[PartyTypeId], [l].[PlotPreRegNo], [l].[ProcedureValue], [l].[ProjectId], [l].[ProjectsId], [l].[PropertyTypeId], [l].[Size], [l].[StatusId], [l].[UnitNumber]

) AS [t]
LEFT JOIN [AspNetUsers] AS [a] ON [t].[AssignedUserId] = [a].[Id]
ORDER BY [t].[Id] DESC

    SELECT [l].[Id], [l].[AssignedUserId], [l].[BuildingName], [l].[BuildingNo], [l].[Code], [l].[CreatedById], [l].[CreatedDate], [l].[CustomFields], [l].[DMSubNumber], [l].[Date], [l].[DeleteDate], [l].[IsActive], [l].[IsDelete], [l].[LandNumber], [l].[Mobile], [l].[ModifiedById], [l].[ModifiedDate], [l].[Name], [l].[PartyTypeId], [l].[PlotPreRegNo], [l].[ProcedureValue], [l].[ProjectId], [l].[ProjectsId], [l].[PropertyTypeId], [l].[Size], [l].[StatusId], [l].[UnitNumber]

) AS [t]
